Hilichurl: Eleka yaya movo Nunu Upano, Upa Gusha boya plata mimi.
English: Now the group moves at night upward, the Green group annoys us.

Hilichurl: Kundala zido Upa Celi boya, yeye beru ika In Upano!
English: The enemy points to the Red group, you all act badly upward!

Hilichurl: Yaya movo Nunu In Upano, Upa Celi boya mani mimi dada.
English: The group moves at night upward, the Red group helps us very well.

Hilichurl: Tomo, mimi muhe beru In Upa Lata boya unta mito dada.
English: Friend, we want to act in the Blue group at noon to know very well.

Hilichurl: Da, Lawa muhe mimi beru dada In Upa Lata boya aba.
English: Yes, the Lord wants us to act very well in the Blue group at dawn.

Hilichurl: Upa Nunu boya muhe mani mimi aba In Upa Gusha boya.
English: The Black group wants to help us at dawn in the Green group.

Hilichurl: Tomo mosi Mita aba, yeye beru In Upa Celi boya aba?
English: Friend eats food at dawn, will you all act in the Red group at dawn?

Hilichurl: Da, odomu biat Upa Celi boya, mimi movo In Upa Unu boya!
English: Yes, the stranger curses the Red group, we will move in the Yellow group!

Hilichurl: Mimi mito Upa Sama mani mimi dada In Upa Gusha boya unta.
English: We know the Shaman group helps us very well in the Green group at noon.

Hilichurl: Lawa, mi muhe Kundala zido Upa Lata boya aba!
English: Lord, I want the enemy to point to the Blue group at dawn!

Hilichurl: Nye tomo, mimi biat Kundala In Upa Lata boya unta.
English: No friend, we will curse the enemy in the Blue group at noon.

Hilichurl: Eleka yaya movo Nunu Upano, Upa Celi boya plata mimi.
English: Now the group moves at night upward, the Red group annoys us.

Hilichurl: Kundala zido Upa Unu boya, yeye beru ika In Upano!
English: The enemy points to the Yellow group, you all act badly upward!

Hilichurl: Tomo mosi Gusha aba, ye mosi Gusha unta mimi nye?
English: Friend eats plants at dawn, will you not eat plants with us at noon?

Hilichurl: Odomu biat Upa Nini boya, mimi biat odomu In Upa Unu boya dada!
English: The stranger curses the Gone group, we curse the stranger in the Yellow group very well!

Hilichurl: Yaya movo Nunu Upano, Upa Unu boya mani mimi dada.
English: The group moves at night upward, the Yellow group helps us very well.

Hilichurl: Lawa, mimi muhe Upa Gusha boya mani ye eleka!
English: Lord, we want the Green group to help you now!

Hilichurl: Tomo, Upa Celi boya beru ika In Upa Sama aba dada nye.
English: Friend, the Red group does not act very badly in the Shaman group at dawn.

Hilichurl: Mimi mosi Mita aba unta, dada, ye mosi Mita dada?
English: We eat food at dawn and noon, very good, do you eat food very well?

Hilichurl: Odomu plata mimi In Upa Unu boya, Lawa muhe biat ye dada!
English: The stranger annoys us in the Yellow group, the Lord really wants to curse you!

Hilichurl: Yeye beru In Upa Lata boya aba, mimi mani ye.
English: You all act in the Blue group at dawn, we will help you.

Hilichurl: Yaya movo Aba Upano, Upa Gusha boya mani mimi dada.
English: The group moves at dawn upward, the Green group helps us very well.

Hilichurl: Tomo mosi Gusha aba, Upa Celi boya mani ye dada.
English: Friend eats plants at dawn, the Red group helps you very well.

Hilichurl: Kundala movo Upano, Upa Unu boya mani Kundala!
English: The enemy moves upward, the Yellow group helps the enemy!

Hilichurl: Tomo mosi Mita aba unta, dada. Mimi muhe mosi Gusha ye dada.
English: Friend eats food at dawn and noon, very good. We really want to eat plants with you.

Hilichurl: Odomu biat Upa Lata boya, Kundala muhe biat mimi!
English: The stranger curses the Blue group, the enemy wants to curse us!

Hilichurl: Lawa, mimi mosi Mita In Upa Nini boya Nunu unta dada.
English: Lord, we eat food in the Gone group at midnight very well.
